snippet: Shi'ite Muslim rebels attacked the home of Yemen's intelligence chief in Sanaa on Saturday, residents and security sources said, showing the fragility of a power-sharing accord that has failed to halt fighting in the capital....

headline.print_headline: Houthi Rebels Attack Yemen Security Chief's Home
headline.main: Houthi Rebels Attack Yemen Security Chief's Home

lead_paragraph: Shi'ite Muslim rebels attacked the home of Yemen's intelligence chief in Sanaa on Saturday, residents and security sources said, showing the fragility of a power-sharing accord that has failed to halt fighting in the capital.
